'''Black knight''' are [[monster|monsters]] who can be found in [[Draynor Village]], their base in the southern part of [[Taverley dungeon]], around the [[Lava Maze]], [[Black Knights' Fortress (location)|Black Knights' Fortress]] which is located north of [[Ice Mountain]], and inside of [[Strange Barrel|Strange Barrels]].

== Background ==
They are members of the Black Knights organization and are part of a large army which has soldiers all over ''[[Runescape Classic]]''. Their history tells of many battles fought against the [[White Knight|White Knights]]. There are several prominent in game NPC's who are part of this army, and are considered Black Knights, such as [[Lord Darquarius]] and [[Iban]].

== Trivia ==
* They once held the title for being the strongest monster in game.

